Projects to demonstrate mixing blazor and MVC
1) mvcblzr: an mvc project that combines the usage of an mvc project with blazor components. Please note that blazor works as component only, they cant have their own page.
2) justblzr: a blazor project with simple blazor components
3) justmvc: an mvc project that references and uses the justblzr project and uses its own endpoints as well
4) features: a shared data access, services and domain project

in order to run it locally just clone it, have a db running on default port 1433 and a database named blzrdb with the associated (or corrected username), then just run dotnet ef database update